{"tid":1540222,"cid":16,"subCid":0,"title":"你唔係以為贏左呀？","createTime":"2019-09-04T11:02:22.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-04T11:04:46.000Z","uid":118941,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"02839cb579e2edc78f9085807075b21e3bb76d37","tid":1540222,"uid":118941,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-04T11:02:22.000Z","msg":"好多人話5大訴求差4個<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">對唔住！係5個佢都無回應</span>。<br />\n<br />\n佢講既撤回係復會之後按議事程序<span style=\"color: red;\">動議</span>撤回條例。<br />\n要開會就有機會比人<span style=\"color: red;\">投反對票</span>。<br />\n咁講居心何在，自己猜測。<br />\n更甚可能佢會話利用<span style=\"color: red;\">二讀</span>，大部分人投反對咪撤回lo。<br />\n然後<span style=\"color: red;\">唔覺意</span>就過半數讚成<span style=\"color: red;\">通過左</span>都唔出奇。<br />\n<br />\n總知，<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">五大訴求，缺一不何<br />\n光復香港，時代革命</span></span>"},{"pid":"844940f21dc69c2f1d08a04e50b23fd6e2769854","tid":1540222,"uid":54226,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-04T11:04:46.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/sv1b7hT.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fsv1b7hT.png&h=9ff09b52&s={SIZE}\" />"}]}